data.description: The Old Ferry Keepers home in Buckingham Landing is now available for purchase. This unique property features 2nd row intracoastal waterway views, 3 bedrooms + Bonus Room, as well as a private over-sized fenced in backyard. The large covered patio & raised deck are great for entertaining. Bring your boat & enjoy the relaxed low country lifestyle in Buckingham Landing. This one-of-a-kind property offers a 4 Car Garage and two rental spaces (In-law suite plus a garage apartment) both separate from main home. This property has the potential for expansion and makes this an extremely rare rental opportunity in the Hilton Head Island area.
